data.description: Experience luxury in this updated waterfront retreat! Inside, discover modern interiors with granite kitchen counters & a chic primary suite w/ lake view, en suite, & brand new California closet walk-in. Enjoy the comfort of the living room, complete with a wood stove, all while taking in the tranquil lake views. Outside, lake front beach that extends into the water, a private dock & redesigned deck w/ hot tub create a personal spa oasis. Includes a carport and two outbuildings for additional storage. Home is wired for Generator. Conveniently located minutes from Belfair & a 35-min commute to PSNS & Bremerton ferries. Optional Hood Canal beach access available for a fee. Indulge in a vacation-like experience every day! Click on video tours!
